title: unfatarians on the SVS IV Festival 2022-05-07

media:group.media:title: unfatarians on the SVS IV Festival 2022-05-07
media:group.media:description:
This is an archive of a SvS (Server vs Server) IV (4th edition) Festival day 2 livestream where my community's EP was played and we were guests on the stream to talk about the process and  explain what are we all about :)

Enormous thanks to Story (the SvS's founder) who's invited us to take part in this charity event and to JohnTheBard who's been a driving force behind the entire unfatarians collaboration.
Also huge thanks to everyone who's contributed and created this EP and for the entire SvS staff for making this possible!

--- TIMESTAMPS:

00:00 - Playing the EP: unfatarians - Secrets
15:53  - Interview with JohnTheBard and unfa
